85
00:09:13,300 --> 00:09:14,900
You follow this?

86
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:16,400
I think so.

87
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:19,200
Look here,
the point I'm making, Carver, is this.

88
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:22,400
Soldiering and policing,
they ain't the same thing.

89
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:24,700
And before we went
and took the wrong turn...

90
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:27,200
