protecting the neighborhood, now, do it?

101
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:13,400
You know the worst thing
about this so-called drug war...

102
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:15,200
to my mind...

103
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:21,600
it <i>just...</i> It ruined this job.

104
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:25,100
Major.

105
