is to go out and get you some kids.

137
00:12:09,900 --> 00:12:11,300
Come on, man.

138
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:13,300
You making it sound easy...

139
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:15,800
but, tell you the truth...

140
00:12:15,900 --> 00:12:18,300
I ain't got no idea
how to go at these hoppers.

141
00:12:18,400 --> 00:12:22,700
Oh, I wouldn't lose any sleep over that.
Nobody else does, neither.

142
00:12:31,100 --> 00:12:32,100
We got one.

143
00:12:33,300 --> 00:12:34,200
His grandmother.

144
00:12:34,300 --> 00:12:35,600
<i>- Looking for me?</i>
<i>- Look, boy...</i>

145
00:12:35,700 --> 00:12:37,900
<i>there's no reason</i>
<i>to leave your clothes in the washer.</i>

