<i>do I have to tell you?</i>

147
00:12:40,100 --> 00:12:42,900
<i>Dag, Mee-maw.</i>
<i>I'm sorry. I just forgot, okay?</i>

148
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:45,100
<i>But I did pick up the laundry soap.</i>
<i>I picked it up.</i>

149
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:47,000
