in the court report.

155
00:13:02,300 --> 00:13:04,200
We're up.

156
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,300
Yeah.

157
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:11,200
Got it right here, yo. Yeah, that's right.

158
00:13:11,300 --> 00:13:14,400
- Major Colvin, Western District.
- Banisky, <i>Sun</i> papers.

159
00:13:15,100 --> 00:13:16,700
So, this your idea?

160
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,300
Got one, get one.

161
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:22,400
Mind if we walk?

162
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:26,300
Apocalypse. Apocalypse.
Got that Apocalypse.

163
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:27,500
Right here, shorty.

164
00:13:27,700 --> 00:13:30,100
