down at headquarters?

168
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:40,700
Look, Command is
well aware of the situation.

169
00:13:40,800 --> 00:13:43,700
While there was some initial <i>concern...</i>

170
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:45,900
But they feel
that the cases we're gonna bring in...

171
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:48,500
- Cases?
- Yeah, prosecutions, sure.

172
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:51,100
