189
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:40,700
I give it to you,
and you run with it right then. Absolutely.

190
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:45,600
A week. But then I gotta run something,
no matter what.

191
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:49,300
- Purple Haze, Purple Haze.
- It's understood.

192
00:14:49,700 --> 00:14:51,600
Right there.

193
00:14:52,500 --> 00:14:55,000
So, brother, what brought you back?

194
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:58,300
It disturbs me to leave business unfinished.

195
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:02,500
Heard you was shot
before you even got started down here.

196
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:04,200
Not like you to get played.

197
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:06,000
Betrayed, you mean.

198
00:15:06,400 --> 00:15:08,700
