199
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:12,000
From his accent, he's homegrown,
raised on the street.

200
00:15:12,100 --> 00:15:15,200
Skilled, intelligent, late 20s, dark...

201
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:19,200
but with a scar across his face, like so.

202
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:23,400
- You down with this nigga?
- I know him.

203
00:15:23,500 --> 00:15:25,200
Not to speak to...

204
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:29,400
