212
00:15:50,500 --> 00:15:52,900
The odds aren't great, but, yeah.

213
00:15:53,100 --> 00:15:54,500
I think it can be done...

214
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:57,300
as long as the thousand things
that can go wrong, don't go wrong.

215
00:15:57,400 --> 00:15:59,000
Even for a white guy?

216
00:15:59,100 --> 00:16:00,700
Even for a white guy.

217
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:02,400
Speaking of which...

218
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:05,900
I notice
a certain monochromatic effect here.

219
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:09,400
One thing we're gonna need
is black faces...

220
00:16:09,500 --> 00:16:11,600
and we're gonna need them
in prominent positions.

221
00:16:11,800 --> 00:16:12,700
You're right.

222
00:16:12,900 --> 00:16:15,200
