00:50:09,600 --> 00:50:14,300
Do not report for a shift until notified.

715
00:50:28,100 --> 00:50:29,900
One more thing, sir.

716
00:50:30,500 --> 00:50:33,300
A <i>Sun</i> reporter is aware of my deployment.

717
00:50:34,200 --> 00:50:36,900
I told him an investigation was pending.

718
00:50:37,100 --> 00:50:39,400
He promised to delay the article.

719
00:50:39,500 --> 00:50:40,700
How long?

720
00:50:41,000 --> 00:50:43,700
About a week, tops.

721
00:50:49,500 --> 00:50:52,600
I was with Superstroke on the pool circuit
in the early days...

722
00:50:52,700 --> 00:50:55,400
but mostly it was
pickpocketing and short cons.

723
00:50:55,500 --> 00:50:59,500
I did the long-distance access card heist
before cell phones got popular.

724
00:50:59,600 --> 00:51:01,200
You crypt numbers?

725
00:51:01,500 --> 00:51:03,800
Yeah, I favored the airports, yeah.

726
00:51:03,900 --> 00:51:06,400
