- Whoa, whoa, what's up with this?

727
00:51:06,500 --> 00:51:08,100
Your man think
I brought him bad merchandise?

728
00:51:08,200 --> 00:51:11,000
'Cause if that what he think,
we can just beat feet right now.

729
00:51:11,100 --> 00:51:15,000
Damn, Bernard, why you acting all CIA
and shit? We trying to make money here.

730
00:51:15,100 --> 00:51:16,500
