733
00:51:24,200 --> 00:51:26,700
Give it a go. Use a cell phone.

734
00:51:37,300 --> 00:51:41,500
Marlene, you send that copy off to Paris?
Thank you, darling.

735
00:51:42,700 --> 00:51:46,000
That will work.
I'm at the airport. The shuttle, yes.

